BEGIN_TEXT
\{ beginproblem() \}
\{ textbook_ref_exact("Rogawski ET 2e", "13.1","30") \}
$PAR
Determine whether \(\bf r_1\) and \(\bf r_2\) collide or intersect:
$BR
\(\bf r\it_1(t)=\left< t,t^2,t^3 \right> \qquad \bf r\it_2(t)=\left< $x, $y, $z \right> \)
$PAR
\{$mc -> print_q \}
\{$mc -> print_a\}
$PAR
\{$mc2 -> print_q \}
\{$mc2 -> print_a\}

$PAR
END_TEXT

